cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) - The paper deals with image-to-image alignment and registration, which is a core problem in computer vision. 
2. cs.RO (Robotics) - Image registration is an important task in robotics, especially for tasks such as visual odometry and SLAM. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper proposes a novel end-to-end network for learning the optimization of image-to-image pose registration, which involves deep learning techniques. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper uses deep learning techniques to improve the accuracy and robustness of image-to-image alignment, which is a key problem in AI. 
5. cs.GR (Graphics) - Image registration is also an important task in computer graphics, especially for tasks such as image stitching and panorama generation.
